293
00:19:35,424 --> 00:19:36,925
Let's go now.

294
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:39,469
All right. Let's go.

295
00:19:40,345 --> 00:19:42,181
You were a math teacher
at Asung High, weren't you?

296
00:19:42,264 --> 00:19:43,599
